%% FixFlow — end-to-end flow map vs storyboard F1–F16
%% Sources: demo video 2026-07-09 · Final storyboard.pdf · repo audit 2026-07-10
%% Read: green = built and verified · amber = partial (exists but optional / manual / backend-only)
%%       red = missing, build it ([P0]/[P1] priority) · purple = current frontend (video) whose source is missing from this repo copy — push it · dashed = storyboard doc debt
%% NOTE: repo frontend is OUTDATED; the video shows the current frontend. Backend facts verified from repo; frontend facts verified from video.
flowchart TD

subgraph LEGEND["Legend"]
direction LR
L1["✅ Built and verified<br/>(in code and/or demo)"]:::built
L2["🟡 Partial — exists but optional,<br/>manual, or backend-only"]:::partial
L3["❌ Missing — build it<br/>[P0] core / [P1] next"]:::missing
L4["🟣 Current frontend (video-verified) —<br/>source not in this repo copy: push it"]:::demoonly
L5["📐 Storyboard debt —<br/>fix the design doc"]:::debt
end

subgraph S1["1 · Launch and intake — F1 to F5"]
direction TB
A1["F1 Jobs list, state-driven CTA per card<br/>tech app: JobsListScreen.tsx"]:::built
A2["F2-F4 intake wizard: Who / What / Where and how<br/>voice-first problem capture, brand alias dropdown —<br/>works in video; source not in repo copy, push it"]:::demoonly
A2b["Web NewJobForm.jsx exists —<br/>plain form, no wizard, no voice"]:::partial
A3["F5 Estimate and review screen<br/>consent chip, review chips"]:::demoonly
G1["[P0] Estimate is not a Job column —<br/>timeline event only, no amount bounds:<br/>demo accepted Rs 50,000 for a fridge"]:::missing
G2["[P0] Approval loop dead-ends:<br/>Ask later never resolves, nothing blocks Start job"]:::missing
G3["[P1] No returning-customer match on phone,<br/>no same-appliance-as-March linking"]:::missing
end

subgraph S2["2 · Job card and travel — F6, F7"]
direction TB
B1["F6 Job card, Start travel CTA<br/>tech app: JobDetailScreen.tsx"]:::built
B2["GPS punches depart_workshop / arrive_customer,<br/>idempotent client_id via outbox — POST /locations"]:::built
B3["Arrival punch UX: Verifying GPS →<br/>Location Verified (demo, 14 min / 4.2 km)"]:::built
G5["🟡 Distance is straight-line derived, no route log;<br/>fuel NOT auto-fed to bill — typed 200 manually in demo"]:::partial
G4["[P1] No approval-pending / est banner on card"]:::missing
G6["[P1] No ETA share, no offline map,<br/>arrival does not start a stopwatch"]:::missing
end

subgraph S3["3 · Arrival evidence gates — F8 · THE core gap"]
direction TB
C1["Backend media pipeline ready: R2 signed PUT,<br/>phases before/after/closing. OLD frontend had capture<br/>tiles (JobMediaCapture.tsx) — absent from current demo:<br/>confirm they survived the rewrite, else rebuild"]:::partial
G7["[P0] No hard gates: serial photo + OCR unit,<br/>condition snaps x2, error-code photo,<br/>BEFORE-video as last gate — all absent or skippable"]:::missing
G8["[P0] Demo captured zero before-evidence:<br/>arrival went straight to a text form —<br/>this is the missing before picture"]:::missing
end

subgraph S4["4 · Work hub — F9"]
direction TB
D1["Work notes + Mark Ready — video-verified<br/>(hold-with-reason: old code only, see regression audit)"]:::built
G9["[P1] Hub has no evidence timeline,<br/>no running timer chip, no problem / est chips"]:::missing
end

subgraph S5["5 · Completion — F10 to F14"]
direction TB
E1["Completion form: materials, time, travel/fuel,<br/>remarks, auto bill — CompleteJobScreen.tsx"]:::built
E2["Voice note upload works —<br/>media phase remark, R2"]:::built
G10["[P0] AFTER-video is not a gate before data entry —<br/>demo submitted completion with zero captures"]:::missing
G11["🟡 Materials = free text + typed prices;<br/>catalog parts and fault/action codes exist<br/>backend-side but no picker UI uses them"]:::partial
G12["[P0] No est-vs-actual pinned —<br/>the estimate never reappears at completion"]:::missing
G13["🟡 Time on-site typed manually (50) —<br/>punches exist but nothing autofills a stopwatch"]:::partial
G14["[P0] Silent edits allowed: 500 x 266 briefly made a<br/>Rs 134,700 bill, corrected with no reason required"]:::missing
end

subgraph S6["6 · Bill and close — F15, F16"]
direction TB
F1n["Bill auto-built, original vs negotiated (paisa ints)<br/>backend endpoints solid: /bill/negotiate, /payments, /void<br/>— UI existed in OLD frontend, unverified in current"]:::partial
F2n["CLOSING-video HARD GATE enforced server-side —<br/>jobs/service.py: cannot close without a closing media row,<br/>offline-tolerant (pending row accepted)"]:::built
F3n["WhatsApp bill message: consent-gated, wa.me v1,<br/>never double-sends, dispatcher default OFF"]:::built
F4n["Evidence-gaps report — closed jobs whose<br/>promised closing video never uploaded"]:::built
G15["🟡 None of this appears in the demo: no bill sheet,<br/>no WhatsApp send, no closed-with-proof card —<br/>the one hard gate that EXISTS was never showcased"]:::partial
G16["[P0] Open blockers from CLAUDE.md:<br/>labour formula TBD, discount-reason wording TBD,<br/>WhatsApp v1 confirm"]:::missing
end

subgraph S7["Cross-cutting"]
direction TB
H1["Attendance: wifi geofence, clock in/out, selfie,<br/>duty pings — in repo and demo'd"]:::built
H2["Offline outbox + idempotent client_id on every<br/>mutation — jobs, punches, media"]:::built
H3["[P1] Urdu bilingual-first — absent in tech app"]:::missing
H5["[P0] Regression audit old vs new frontend:<br/>media capture tiles, negotiate/payments/void UI,<br/>hold-with-reason — all in old code, none visible<br/>in the current demo. List what the rewrite dropped"]:::missing
H4["[P0 demo hygiene] Purge dummy/offensive seed data<br/>(job 1054 customer name) and re-record ONE clean<br/>job start-to-finish following this map"]:::missing
end

subgraph S8["📐 Storyboard debt — fix the doc, not just the code"]
direction TB
P1["Approval loop unstoryboarded: who resolves Ask later,<br/>where, and what it blocks"]:::debt
P2["Before-video is a buried checkbox row in F8 while<br/>after-video gets a full screen (F10) —<br/>give before-video its own gate screen; the dev missed it"]:::debt
P3["No actor swimlanes — desk (F1-F5) vs technician (F6-F16)<br/>read as one user"]:::debt
P4["GPS-fail / offline unhappy path and<br/>pause / awaiting-part branch not storyboarded"]:::debt
P5["Two near-duplicate storyboards in one PDF,<br/>no canonical marker"]:::debt
end

S1 --> S2 --> S3 --> S4 --> S5 --> S6
S6 -.->|"peak-end: paid · proof attached · back to list (F16)"| S1
S8 -.- S1

classDef built fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,stroke-width:2px,color:#14532d
classDef partial fill:#fef9c3,stroke:#ca8a04,stroke-width:2px,color:#713f12
classDef missing fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,stroke-width:2px,color:#7f1d1d
